<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="universal-adj">universal <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌjuːnɪ'vɜːsl/    美 /ˌjuːnɪ'vɜːrsl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>普遍的；通用的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>universal truth</strong> 
普遍真理</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>全世界的；全体的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>universal languages 
世界通用语言</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Envy is a universal weakness of people. 
嫉妒是人们共同的弱点。</p></div></div>